{"tid":105850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次上女朋友屋企食飯見家長 有咩要注意？","createTime":"2017-02-03T08:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T12:52:28.000Z","uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9558114fceb9c53561881c990503d6a2535ff671","tid":105850,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊咗幾個月<br />\n佢老豆話要我上去食餐飯<br />\n我要注意或者準備啲咩？<br />\n好驚佢老豆唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關我個樣一睇就成個玩女mk仔咁<br />\n我女朋友就乖乖女type<br />\n我頭髮仲要係藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟我應該點樣萬全準備嚟應對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4500ab875fd41914e271a9f894232e1c3be6a098","tid":105850,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"藍色頭髮 死MK"},{"pid":"e2fb82cda5274206b2766c9585b21dec2847d95d","tid":105850,"uid":76167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"7e50c017046959900202769a7454f72096794875","tid":105850,"uid":29621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"第一次上人屋企記得買禮<br />\n買兩盒安全套<br />\n一盒擺條女間房用<br />\n一盒送比佢老豆<br />\n包無死<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 無送過安全套"},{"pid":"1f3594018db72dae551b92e3afd52923a2e06662","tid":105850,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍色頭髮 死MK</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f96e3e61b9c60fb856dec76a38e83b4477ff1dc","tid":105850,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2